Library of MTK logo showing, including kernel logo and charging animation.

WHAT IT DOES?
=============
libshowlogo.so is an important module of kernel logo and charging animation,
encapsulates zlib decompress method and some common method of drawing picture.

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1. libcutils.so
2. libutils.so
3. libc.so
4. libstdc++.so
5. libdl.so
6. liblog.so
7. libz.so
8. libgui.so
9. libui.so

[Build Method]
mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/external/libshowlogo

HOW TO USE IT?
==============
Is called by boot_logo_updater, charger and ipod.